title: 10 Takeaways from Week 8!
itunes:title: 10 Takeaways from Week 8!
description:
Daniel Jeremiah & Bucky Brooks share their biggest takeaways from an exciting Week 8 of action, including an instant reaction of the Browns firing head coach Hue Jackson and offensive coordinator Todd Haley (:30). After, the guys discuss the quarterback duel in LA (7:00), the Eagles' rejuvenated run game, which helped them win in London (9:50), the Colts are finally keeping Luck clean & safe in the pocket (12:15), Jameis Winston's time in Tampa is ticking (18:35) & lastly, AP is EATING (27:15)!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
